<div id="info-page">

	<h1> Tell Your Member of Congress to Support Strong Gainful Employment Regulations</h1>


	<div class="description" id="description">
		<p>&#160;<span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Far too many students graduate from for-profit colleges with enormous amounts of debt and are not getting the skills they need to be successful in today’s workforce. They can’t find a job, they default on their loans, and taxpayers’ dollars have been wasted in the process, while these institutions continue to profit off of student debt.</span></span>&#160;<span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;"> </span></span></p>
<p></p>
<p></p>
<p><span style="font-size: x-large;"><span style="font-family: Calibri; font-weight: bold; vertical-align: baseline; white-space: pre-wrap;">Tell your representative to ensure that career education programs are providing students with gainful employment in a recognized occupation. You can use the letter we provided below, or customize your own.</span></span></p>
	</div>
</div>

<div id="mainForm">
<form action="/p/dia/action3/common/public/blinded/blind_submit.sjs" method="POST" onsubmit="return submitForm(this);">
